# Event System Conventions

- Use `agrogame.events.EventBus` and `BaseEvent` across modules; emit minimal payload.
- Handlers must be fast; avoid cross-module state mutation.
- Prefer module-local events; keep contracts stable and documented.
- All events are debug-logged at emit; leverage for troubleshooting.

See: [agrogame/events/](mdc:agrogame/events/bus.py)
